STATE
v.
Monica D. BRANCH. No. 95P04-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 20, 2006. Barbara S. Blackman, Assistant Appellate Defender, for Monica D. Branch. Belinda J. Foster, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 19th day of April 2006 by Attorney General for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 20th day of April 2006."
